## âš™ï¸ **Installation & Setup**

---

## **1ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Karthik-hr18/AI_DOCUMENT_SUMMARIZER.git
cd AI_DOCUMENT_SUMMARIZER
```

---

# ğŸ–¥ï¸ **Frontend Setup**

### 1. Install dependencies

```bash
cd FrontEnd
npm install
```

### 2. Start the development server

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

# ğŸ **Backend Setup (FastAPI)**

### 1. Create a virtual environment

```bash
cd Backend
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Mac/Linux
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows
```

### 2. Install backend dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Run the FastAPI server

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Backend runs at:
ğŸ‘‰ [http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000)

Docs:
ğŸ“˜ [http://localhost:8000/docs](http://localhost:8000/docs)

---

## ğŸ”‘ **Environment Variables**

Create a `.env` file inside the **Backend** folder:

```
SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@localhost/ai_summarizer_db
```

Frontend `.env`:

```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
```

---

## ğŸ“¡ **API Endpoints (FastAPI)**

### **Auth**

| Method | Endpoint       | Description           |
| ------ | -------------- | --------------------- |
| POST   | /auth/register | Register new user     |
| POST   | /auth/login    | Login + get JWT token |

### **Document**

| Method | Endpoint   | Description             |
| ------ | ---------- | ----------------------- |
| POST   | /upload    | Upload document         |
| POST   | /summarize | Get AI summary          |
| GET    | /history   | Get userâ€™s past uploads |

---

## ğŸ³ **Run with Docker**

### Build

```bash
cd Backend
docker build -t ai-summarizer-backend .
```

### Run

```bash
docker run -p 8000:8000 ai-summarizer-backend
```

